<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.8.1">
<l>muṭiyāṉē mūvulakun toḻutēt tuñcī</l>
<l>raṭiyāṉē yāḻkaṭalaik kaṭaintāy puḷḷūr</l>
<l>koṭiyāṉē koṇṭal vaṇṇā vaṇṭat tumpari</l>
<l>ṉeṭiyāṉē yeṉṟu kiṭakkumeṉ ṉeñcamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My heart reposes saying “you with the crown,</l>
<l>you with the excellent foot that the three worlds worship [and] praise,</l>
<l>you who churned the deep ocean, you with a banner mounted by the bird,</l>
<l>you of cloud colour, Tall one beyond the egg[-shaped universe].”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
